==Latin==
===Etymology===
Adverbial form of Latin [[Romanicus]].

===Adverb===
'''romanice'''
# In the [[Roman]] manner.
# ''(Medieval Latin)'' In a Romance language.

===Derivatives===
*[[romance]]

